blog.name: poppingpunksbubble
blog.title: (un)lost
blog.description: men in pop culture films are my weakness.

body:
theory for A4

you know when dr. strange says there’s only one possible way for them to win and beat thanos and when they go with that plan and it all turns to shit??

WELL what if that was supposed to happen?!

i mean, strange does say there was no other way to tony before he is dusted and strange did see a gazillion other possible outcomes.

SO,, this whole “everybody dying” thing could have just been a way to get the original avengers back to together so they can work as a damn team again and properly defeat thanos.


(and i’m kinda hoping captain marvel just turns up and shows them how it’s done when she defeats thanos like the bad bitch she is)

So badass.
